Class EntityFunction

    • jalse.entities.functions.EntityFunction

    public class EntityFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.function.Function<java.lang.reflect.Method,EntityMethod>
    A function for a specific Entity type. This can beused by an InvocationHandler to translate original method calls to the desired EntityMethod.
